        "text": "was a pretty huge thing for biology but",
        "start": 9.12,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "you know what else was huge",
        "start": 11.519,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "the equipment once they made it into the",
        "start": 12.96,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "lab those big",
        "start": 15.2,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "bulky sequencing machines were never",
        "start": 16.08,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "leaving the workbench again",
        "start": 18.48,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "and they were expensive only some labs",
        "start": 20.16,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "could afford them which left",
        "start": 22.64,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "some biologists out in the cold those",
        "start": 24.0,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "who rely on field work for their science",
        "start": 25.92,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "had to think carefully",
        "start": 28.16,
        "duration": 2.959
    },
    {
