        "start": 29.519,
        "duration": 4.481
    },
    {
        "text": "lab but technology has come a long way",
        "start": 31.119,
        "duration": 4.801
    },
    {
        "text": "and some of those hulking benchtop",
        "start": 34.0,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "machines are now",
        "start": 35.92,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "pocket-sized and affordable which means",
        "start": 37.36,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "for the first time",
        "start": 40.079,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "researchers can bring the genetics lab",
        "start": 41.28,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "to the field",
        "start": 43.76,
        "duration": 2.959
    },
    {
        "text": "they can sample to their heart's content",
        "start": 44.8,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "even in remote underexplored locations",
        "start": 46.719,
        "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
        "text": "places where there is a lot of life",
        "start": 49.44,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "waiting to be discovered",
        "start": 51.84,
        "duration": 3.359
    },
    {
        "text": "first let's look at a tool that isn't",
        "start": 53.199,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "used in the field yet but can make",
        "start": 55.199,
        "duration": 2.961
    },
    {
        "text": "fieldwork much",
        "start": 57.12,
        "duration": 4.079
    },
    {
        "text": "easier a microarray is a tool used to",
        "start": 58.16,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "detect the expression of",
        "start": 61.199,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "thousands of genes at the same time so",
        "start": 62.8,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "researchers can learn a lot about one",
        "start": 65.36,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "organism",
        "start": 67.36,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "or an entire population from a single",
        "start": 68.08,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "sample microarrays are",
        "start": 70.56,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "slides that are printed with tens of",
        "start": 72.08,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "thousands of tiny spots of dna in",
        "start": 74.0,
        "duration": 4.479
    },
    {
        "text": "specific positions those bits of dna",
        "start": 76.08,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "can match up with messenger rna in a",
        "start": 78.479,
        "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
        "text": "sample since mrna is made when genes are",
        "start": 80.72,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "expressed",
        "start": 83.6,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "microarrays tell us which genes in a",
        "start": 84.32,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "sample are",
        "start": 86.88,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "active and which aren't these tools are",
        "start": 87.6,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "relatively accessible and rely",
        "start": 89.68,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "on open source software so you don't",
        "start": 91.36,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "have to blow all your funding to use",
        "start": 93.36,
        "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
        "text": "them while these aren't used directly in",
        "start": 95.119,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "the field at least not yet",
        "start": 97.119,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "microarrays make field research better",
        "start": 98.799,
        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "and",
        "start": 101.439,
        "duration": 2.401
    },
    {
        "text": "faster knowing what genes are being",
        "start": 101.84,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "expressed by what organisms",
        "start": 103.84,
        "duration": 3.919
    },
    {
        "text": "can tell us what's out there but it also",
        "start": 105.84,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "gives us information about the genetic",
        "start": 107.759,
        "duration": 4.241
    },
    {
        "text": "variety of an ecosystem and even how",
        "start": 109.439,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "creatures are responding to",
        "start": 112.0,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "environmental changes",
        "start": 113.439,
        "duration": 2.801
    },
    {
        "text": "this is particularly important in the",
        "start": 114.72,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "face of climate change and there's more",
        "start": 116.24,
        "duration": 2.879
    },
    {
        "text": "than one tool for that",
        "start": 117.92,
        "duration": 2.559
    },
    {
        "text": "say you need to keep an eye on what's in",
        "start": 119.119,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "the water for example to predict",
        "start": 120.479,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "harmful algal blooms which are becoming",
        "start": 122.399,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "more common as our climate warms",
        "start": 124.64,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "if you could detect the algae's genetic",
        "start": 126.399,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "material ahead of time",
        "start": 128.319,
        "duration": 2.881
    },
    {
        "text": "you might be able to see the bloom",
        "start": 129.759,
        "duration": 3.361
    },
    {
        "text": "coming before you're up to your waste in",
        "start": 131.2,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "it",
        "start": 133.12,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "environmental sample processors or esps",
        "start": 133.36,
        "duration": 5.28
    },
    {
        "text": "are genetic sensors that can be placed",
        "start": 136.56,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "in a body of water like a lake",
        "start": 138.64,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "river or ocean they can stay submerged",
        "start": 140.56,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "for months",
        "start": 143.04,
        "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
        "text": "letting researchers collect and analyze",
        "start": 144.0,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "multiple water samples",
        "start": 146.239,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "the esp samples the water and then uses",
        "start": 147.76,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "a bunch of molecular probes",
        "start": 150.16,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "to identify the genetic material that's",
        "start": 151.84,
        "duration": 3.119
    },
    {
        "text": "there these probes",
        "start": 153.76,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "are simply tiny bits of dna or rna that",
        "start": 154.959,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "compare",
        "start": 157.76,
        "duration": 2.559
    },
    {
        "text": "with the genetic material researchers",
        "start": 158.56,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "are looking for the instrument can be",
        "start": 160.319,
        "duration": 3.041
    },
    {
        "text": "accessed remotely which allows",
        "start": 161.84,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "researchers to download and analyze data",
        "start": 163.36,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "in",
        "start": 165.68,
        "duration": 2.559
    },
    {
        "text": "almost real time without removing the",
        "start": 165.92,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "instrument the researchers can tell the",
        "start": 168.239,
        "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
        "text": "esp to take more samples when it detects",
        "start": 169.84,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "water conditions would trigger a bloom",
        "start": 172.08,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "for example a sudden drop in water",
        "start": 173.76,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "temperature that means nutrient-rich",
        "start": 176.0,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "bottom water is moving up to the surface",
        "start": 177.68,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "this helps researchers pinpoint when",
        "start": 179.76,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "just a few harmful algal cells will turn",
        "start": 181.28,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "into a bloom",
        "start": 183.92,
        "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
        "text": "making esps useful as early warning",
        "start": 185.12,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "monitoring systems for coastal waters",
        "start": 187.519,
        "duration": 4.401
    },
    {
        "text": "currently esps only function in shallow",
        "start": 189.519,
        "duration": 4.321
    },
    {
        "text": "water and at mild temperatures but",
        "start": 191.92,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "researchers are working on modifying",
        "start": 193.84,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "them to be able to stand up to the",
        "start": 195.28,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "intense pressures and sometimes",
        "start": 196.48,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "extreme temperatures of the deep sea",
        "start": 198.08,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "they hope to deploy them near deep sea",
        "start": 200.159,
        "duration": 3.601
    },
    {
        "text": "hydrothermal vents to find out who's",
        "start": 201.68,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "living around there possibly capturing",
        "start": 203.76,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "genetic material from new",
        "start": 205.68,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "never-before-seen creatures but while",
        "start": 207.44,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "molecular probes require you to design",
        "start": 209.28,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "them based on what you're looking for",
        "start": 211.68,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "the real dream",
        "start": 213.28,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "is to be able to scan your surroundings",
        "start": 214.56,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "and sequence the dna of whatever you",
        "start": 216.56,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "find on the spot which is no longer",
        "start": 218.64,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "limited to the likes of star trek",
        "start": 220.799,
        "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
        "text": "a device called the min ion it allows",
        "start": 222.72,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "researchers",
        "start": 225.599,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "to sequence the long dna or rna",
        "start": 226.4,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "fragments in real time",
        "start": 228.959,
        "duration": 4.081
    },
    {
        "text": "using technology that can fit in your",
        "start": 230.799,
        "duration": 4.321
    },
    {
        "text": "pocket this type of sequencing works by",
        "start": 233.04,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "passing nucleic acids through a tiny",
        "start": 235.12,
        "duration": 3.679
    },
    {
        "text": "hole called a nanopore",
        "start": 237.04,
        "duration": 3.839
    },
    {
        "text": "as each base passes through there's a",
        "start": 238.799,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "slight change in electrical current the",
        "start": 240.879,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "electrical signal produced gets decoded",
        "start": 242.879,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "by the device in real time",
        "start": 245.04,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "providing the specific dna or rna",
        "start": 246.799,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "sequence it",
        "start": 249.28,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "sounds like the future this technique",
        "start": 250.159,
        "duration": 4.481
    },
    {
        "text": "makes dna sequencing",
        "start": 253.28,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "very easy to do in the field where",
        "start": 254.64,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "before samples would need to be",
        "start": 256.72,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "preserved and processed later in the lab",
        "start": 258.16,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "it's especially useful when looking at",
        "start": 260.4,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "environmental dna in the water",
        "start": 262.24,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "to see what creatures are out there this",
        "start": 264.24,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "new technology is also",
        "start": 266.16,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "much more affordable than older",
        "start": 267.759,
        "duration": 3.361
    },
    {
        "text": "sequencing technologies",
        "start": 269.68,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "priced about the same as an iphone in",
        "start": 271.12,
        "duration": 4.639
    },
    {
        "text": "fact there's even a companion app that",
        "start": 273.919,
        "duration": 3.921
    },
    {
        "text": "makes analyzing the sequenced dna",
        "start": 275.759,
        "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
        "text": "easy to do right in the field among",
        "start": 277.84,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "other things it makes it possible to",
        "start": 279.6,
        "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
        "text": "transfer data from the sequencer without",
        "start": 281.28,
        "duration": 3.919
    },
    {
        "text": "an internet connection",
        "start": 283.759,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "meaning nowhere is too remote for",
        "start": 285.199,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "genetic sequencing",
        "start": 287.44,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "high-tech genetic advancements have",
        "start": 288.639,
        "duration": 4.081
    },
    {
        "text": "dramatically improved field biology",
        "start": 290.24,
        "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
        "text": "they require less time space and money",
        "start": 292.72,
        "duration": 6.16
    },
    {
        "text": "all while bringing the genetics lab to",
        "start": 296.24,
        "duration": 4.239
    },
    {
        "text": "the field they've helped researchers",
        "start": 298.88,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "take more samples and look at their data",
        "start": 300.479,
        "duration": 3.841
    },
    {
        "text": "almost immediately to give them a more",
        "start": 302.24,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "in-depth look at the ecosystem they're",
        "start": 304.32,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "studying these technologies can be used",
        "start": 306.32,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "in underexplored locations giving",
        "start": 308.32,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "scientists a better understanding of who",
        "start": 310.16,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "is living there meaning they could help",
        "start": 312.08,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "us discover new species or answer",
        "start": 313.36,
        "duration": 4.399
    },
    {
        "text": "questions we haven't even thought of yet",
        "start": 315.44,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
